highlights.text: “Slaughter Of The Soul” by At The Gates is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Finland, up 38 spots at #33.
“Mun ihminen” by ELLIMEI has been on Viral Songs Finland the longest, at 143 days straight.
EsDeeKid has the most spots on Viral Songs Finland. “Phantom” is the highest at #26.
“Oot mun seikkailu” by Sofia Noir is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Finland at #1.
